<L>__{exterior courtyard night}
<A>__{there on the concrete below, face down, is the body of luther coleman. hooker races out to it and kneels down.}
<C>__{hooker}
<P>__{(shaking the body)}
<D>__{c'mon luther, get up. you gotta get up, luther.}
<A>__{in the distance, sirens are heard. heads are out of the windows and some people are starting to gather in the courtyard.}
<C>__{hooker }
<D>__{goddamn you, luther, will you get up?}
<P>__{(pounding on the body)}
<D>__{i'm not waitin' for you, luther. i'm not waitin' anymore. get up, you son of a bitch. goddamn you, luther, goddamn.}
<A>__{the sirens are close now, and hooker tears himself away from luther and runs. the others gather to look at the body.}
